# Bali ViewComponents Library

**AFAL's open-source ViewComponent library** providing 40+ reusable UI components for Rails applications.

## Quick Start

Add to your Gemfile:

```ruby
gem 'bali'
```

Then in your view:

```erb
<%%= render Bali::Button::Component.new(name: 'Save', variant: :primary) %>
```

