## Component Categories

### Layout Components
Cards, Columns, Drawer, Modal, PageHeader, Hero

### Navigation Components
NavBar, SideMenu, Breadcrumb, Tabs, Dropdown, Stepper

### Data Display Components
Table, DataTable, List, Timeline, Progress, Avatar, Tag

### Interactive Components
Button, Link, SearchInput, Carousel, Tooltip, Calendar

### Form Components
All form elements with consistent styling

### Feedback Components
Notification, FlashNotifications, Loader, Message

